      <li style="padding:0.5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1A3A1A;"><a href="/should-i-use-claude-or-chatgpt" style="color:#00C853;text-decoration:none;">Should I use Claude or ChatGPT? (decision tool) →</a></li>
      <li style="padding:0.5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1A3A1A;"><a href="/cost-of-not-using-ai" style="color:#00C853;text-decoration:none;">The cost of not using AI →</a></li>
      <li style="padding:0.5rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1A3A1A;"><a href="/how-much-does-ai-implementation-cost" style="color:#00C853;text-decoration:none;">How much does AI implementation cost? →</a></li>
      <li style="padding:0.5rem 0;"><a href="/the-90-day-ai-rollout-playbook" style="color:#00C853;text-decoration:none;">The 90-day AI rollout playbook →</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
