    <div class="cta-box">
      <div>
        <div class="cta-text">Want to actually capture this ROI?</div>
        <div class="cta-sub">The $1,500 AI Audit produces a written roadmap targeting your highest-leverage workflows. Most clients hit 60%+ capture rate within 90 days.</div>
      </div>
